subject: Tennis
French Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Eugenie Bouchard, who reached the final at Wimbledon last year, lost for the eighth time in nine matches. Grigor Dimitrov, known for his stylish game, was ousted by the American Jack Sock.
